First listed as an unincorporated place which included [[Bessmay, Texas|Bessmay]] in the [[1970 U.S. census]]<ref name=1970CensusTX/> and appeared as the Bessmay-Buna [[census designated place]] in the [[1980 United States census]].<ref name=1980CensusTX/> In the [[1990 U.S. census]] the CDP was renamed the Buna CDP.<ref name=1990CensusTX/>

